sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant Nginx as Nginx (Reverse Proxy)
    participant Express as Express (API Server)
    participant SocketIO as Socket.IO (Real-time)
    participant MySQL as MySQL (Database)
    participant Redis as Redis (Cache)
    participant InfluxDB as InfluxDB (Analytics)
    participant S3 as S3 (Storage)
    participant Docker as Docker (Sandbox)

    User->>Nginx: HTTPS Request (API/Static)
    Nginx->>Express: Proxy Request
    Express->>MySQL: Query Persistent Data
    Express->>Redis: Check Cache/State
    Express->>InfluxDB: Log Activity Metrics
    Express->>S3: Upload/Download Files
    Express-->>Nginx: Response
    Nginx-->>User: Deliver Content

    User->>SocketIO: WebSocket Connection
    SocketIO->>Redis: Get Real-time State
    SocketIO->>Express: Verify JWT
    Express-->>SocketIO: Auth Status
    SocketIO->>Docker: Execute Code (Sandbox)
    Docker-->>SocketIO: Execution Results
    SocketIO->>User: Real-time Updates